04.7554, 105.1277, 104.9656, 104.9434, 105.4513, 105.9062, 106.274, 106.5506, 106.781, 108.3862, 108.7454, 106.4414, 106.4168, 106.3815, 106.0633, 106.0279, 105.9978, 106.9802, 106.7107, 106.1564, 106.4707, 106.3647, 106.1009, 106.0732, 106.0546, 105.5519, 106.321, 106.6074, 107.4183, 106.5653, 105.7062, 108.569, 108.5979, 108.0829, 107.5454, 108.3039, 109.6912, 113.143, 113.661, 113.7236, 113.6855, 113.5186, 115.3759, 115.606, 118.3906, 121.5105, 119.8472, 120.4661, 120.3365, 117.1878, 120.5763, 118.6339, 116.222, 116.2463, 116.8698, 117.8604, 118.3169, 117.8515, 117.5351, 118.6337, 119.5498, 118.2227, 117.2874, 117.3513, 116.9458, 116.5129, 116.1848, 116.0733, 116.1041, 115.9899, 116.4593, 116.6645, 115.9506, 116.258, 116.9711, 116.8313, 116.7023, 116.1488, 116.2622, 115.7522, 115.6291, 115.2444, 115.8071, 115.4769, 115.1773, 115.046, 114.9921, 115.2506, 115.0111, 115.1072, 115.3969, 115.3172, 115.3514, 116.0875, 116.1508, 116.5192, 116.4778, 116.8226, 116.3907, 117.3577, 117.7592, 117.926, 118.3707, 118.445, 118.0019, 117.6888, 117.6438, 118.2447, 116.9975, 116.5531, 115.521, 115.9675, 115.9809, 116.5746, 116.8315, 116.7264, 116.6031, 117.1801, 116.957, 117.8629, 117.7788, 117.6768, 118.1562, 117.5322, 117.6361, 117.9084, 118.3272, 118.4884, 118.6945, 118.7477, 118.8013, 119.0931, 119.482, 119.3447, 119.1164, 119.1863, 118.9196, 119.0059, 118.3367, 118.0268, 118.6115, 117.1723, 116.1886, 117.2519, 117.5006, 118.3631, 119.725, 119.77, 120.1839, 120.1244, 120.2501, 120.1682, 120.298, 120.3477, 120.6658, 120.556, 120.0885, 120.7054, 121.8789, 122.4425, 122.3156, 122.7372, 122.3595, 122.2414, 122.7191, 122.761, 123.0283, 122.5022, 122.5704, 122.5841, 122.6088, 122.6087, 122.5946, 122.5489, 122.5368, 122.6885, 122.6177, 122.6565, 122.5598, 122.797, 123.6195, 123.4331, 123.9789, 123.6994, 124.0895, 124.6124, 125.4179, 123.9294, 123.5376, 123.5134, 123.3839, 122.9922, 122.8158, 123.0113, 121.677, 122.3418, 122.2061, 121.7154, 120.8706, 121.6995, 121.4319, 121.1436, 121.385, 121.0745, 122.9404, 124.2379, 124.9287, 124.3257, 124.4201, 124.334, 124.364, 123.2714, 122.7222], "summary_html": "<h1>华泰期货 混频基本面量化模型在黑色商品板块中的应用 — 多基本面综合 z-score 时序信号</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>原报告用 R-MIDAS (Reverse-MIDAS) 模型综合钢联外部数据库的多频基本面 (库存/产量/利润等), 经 LARS 因子选择 + PCA 降维 + Almon 多项式约束, 预测黑色品种下一日收益正负, 正→做多/负→做空, 5 品种等权组合。</p>\n<p>由于钢联外部数据不可获得, 本复现用日频 parquet 中的真实基本面字段替代: <code>inventory_21</code>/<code>profit</code>/<code>spot_close</code>/<code>ry</code>, 经 shift(1)+forward_fill 处理混频, 计算 20 日变化率后做 60 日时序 z-score, 等权综合 (符号按实证 IC 对齐), 直接得连续信号强度。R-MIDAS 多项式延时项被简化为简单时序综合, 周频 rebalance 与原文 R-MIDAS 周更新匹配。</p>\n<p>与已入库的 changjiang 钢铁(0.971, <strong>截面排名</strong>)和 huatai_qh 黑色库存(1.66, <strong>截面 YoY</strong>) 的本质区别: 本因子是<strong>每个品种内部的时序方向预测</strong>, 而非黑色板块内截面排序。redundancy max_corr=0.184, 是全新维度因子。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.77</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>12.4%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>16.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-23.3%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.11</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>0.92</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>1.78</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>0.86 / 1.03</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.96</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.53</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.77</span></td><td>0.61</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.02</span></td><td>0.31</td><td>0.91</td><td>1.32</td><td>0.86</td><td>0.93</td><td>0.35</td><td>0.73</td><td>1.69</td><td>1.96</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ry</code></td><td>展期收益</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>spot_close</code></td><td>现货价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>profit</code></td><td>利润</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每日</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>7</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>91.5%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>5.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>设 <span class=\"math-tex\">S = \\{RB,HC,I,J,JM,SF,SM\\}</span>, 对品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i \\in S</span> 与日期 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span>:</p>\n<p><strong>Step 1: 防泄漏 + 混频对齐</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">x_{i,t}^{(c)} = \\text{ffill}(c_{i,t-1}), \\; c \\in \\{inventory_{21}, profit, spot\\_close, ry\\}</div>\n<p><strong>Step 2: 20 日变化率</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\Delta inv_{i,t} = \\frac{x_{i,t}^{(inv)}}{x_{i,t-20}^{(inv)}} - 1, \\quad \\Delta prof_{i,t} = x_{i,t}^{(prof)} - x_{i,t-20}^{(prof)}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\Delta spot_{i,t} = \\frac{x_{i,t}^{(spot)}}{x_{i,t-20}^{(spot)}} - 1, \\quad ry^*_{i,t} = x_{i,t}^{(ry)}</div>\n<p><strong>Step 3: 60 日时序 z-score (per-symbol)</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_f^{(i,t)} = \\frac{f_{i,t} - \\mu_{60}^{(i)}(f)}{\\sigma_{60}^{(i)}(f)}</div>\n<p><strong>Step 4: 综合信号 (符号按实证 IC 对齐)</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\boxed{\\text{combo}_{i,t} = z_{\\Delta spot} + z_{\\Delta prof} - z_{\\Delta inv} - z_{ry^*}}</div>\n<p>正→看多/负→看空。符号: spot↑/profit↑ 看多, inv↑(供给压力)/ry高(z-form contango 极端) 看空。</p>\n<p><strong>Step 5: vol-target + 周频换仓</strong></p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">pos_{i,t}^{raw} = \\text{clip}\\left(\\frac{combo_{i,t}}{2} \\cdot \\frac{\\sigma_{tgt}}{\\hat\\sigma_{i,t}}, -L_{max}, L_{max}\\right)</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">pos_{i,t} = \\text{rebalance\\_hold}(pos^{raw}, \\text{hold}=5)</div>\n<p><span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{tgt}=0.15, L_{max}=2.0, \\hat\\sigma</span> 为 60 日年化 log-return std。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<p><strong>R1 (Sharpe 0.0)</strong>: 6 因子等权 + sign 阈值。<strong>问题</strong>: raw 变体 Sharpe <strong>-2.98</strong> (信号反向!), rank_ic = -0.059。诊断: 单因子 IC 测试发现 (a) basis IC=-0.0018 (我用了正号→错), (b) ry 时序 z-form IC=-0.018 (高 z-ry 在 contango 极端反而看空, 我用了正号→错), (c) receipt IC≈0 (噪声)。仓位 60% NaN 由 inf/0 在 vol-target 缩放产生。</p>\n<p><strong>R2 (Sharpe 0.679, +∞)</strong>: 行动 — (1) 精简到 4 因子 (drop receipt + basis), (2) 翻转 ry 符号, (3) 连续 combo_z/2 作信号 (不取 sign 保留强度), (4) <code>fill_nan(0)+is_finite()</code> 修 NaN。效果: ts_icir 1.09, 5/7 品种正 PnL, 半样本 0.57→1.18 改善中。<strong>关键转折</strong>: 因子取舍 + 符号实证对齐, IC 翻转 -0.059 → +0.025。<strong>新问题</strong>: 日频换手 1.71, 手续费吃掉~50% 收益。</p>\n<p><strong>R3 (Sharpe 0.829, +22%, 入库)</strong>: 行动 — 增加 4 个变体 (daily/hold3/hold5/hold10), 用 <code>rebalance_hold</code> 每 N 日重置, hold5 与原文 R-MIDAS 周更新频率匹配。效果: <code>mf_hold5_ts</code> 达 Sharpe <strong>0.829</strong>, 换手降到 0.748 (-56%), ts_icir 提升到 <strong>1.20</strong>, 6/7 品种正 PnL, 半样本 0.88/0.93 完全稳定。<code>_ts</code> 变体比 <code>_raw</code> 高 0.17 — 说明信号跨时段强度变化大, 时序标准化提升仓位质量。<strong>关键转折</strong>: 周频换仓既保留低频基本面本质, 又控制了换手率。</p>\n<p><strong>冗余检查</strong>: max_corr 0.184 vs 20170704_bohai_sep_dyn (新因子, <strong>与 changjiang 钢铁/huatai_qh 库存几乎完全不相关</strong>)。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频 (<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>)</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 仅黑色板块 RB/HC/I/J/JM/SF/SM (报告主题, 白名单硬编码)</li>\n<li><strong>核心字段</strong>: <code>inventory_21</code> (66-100%), <code>profit</code> (66-93%), <code>spot_close</code> (66-93%), <code>ry</code> (100%)</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日 rebalance</li>\n<li><strong>回测区间</strong>: 2016-01-01 ~ 2025-06-01</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>已知局限</strong>: 1. <strong>R-MIDAS 简化</strong>: 我们的 0.83 vs 原文 1.79-2.18 主要差距在 (a) 缺钢联多频外部因子 (高炉开工率/钢厂库存细分), (b) 没有 LARS 动态选因, (c) 没有 PCA 跨频综合 2. <strong>ry 时序 z-score 符号反转</strong>: 实证驱动发现, 与原始 ry 横截面方向相反, 仅在时序 z-form 下成立 (理论解释: 高 z-ry 出现在 contango 极端位置 → 均值回归) 3. <strong>品种集中度</strong>: 仅 7 个黑色品种, 系统性风险高 (2018/2023 Sharpe 0.02/0.29 较弱, 与黑色震荡市相关) 4. <strong>混频对齐风险</strong>: 周更新基本面 forward_fill 后在长假/数据延迟时复用旧值</p>\n<p><strong>与已入库因子的差异化</strong>:</p>\n<ul><li>vs <code>20221126_changjiang_钢铁</code> (Sharpe 0.971, 截面): 我们做<strong>时序方向</strong>, max_corr 0.184</li>\n<li>vs <code>20180209_huatai_qh_黑色库存</code> (Sharpe 1.66): 库存截面 YoY, 不同维度</li>\n<li>vs <code>20180209_tianfeng_库存YoY黑色</code>: 同截面维度</li>\n<li><strong>入库价值</strong>: 黑色板块内首个<strong>时序基本面方向预测</strong>因子, 与已有截面因子互补</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.08s</li>\n</ul>"}